Class Frog

  • java.lang.Object
    • Frog
  • public class Frog
extends java.lang.Object
    The class models Frog objects with one int variable for weight. A frog has no legs if its weight is at most 5 (MAX_WEIGHT_FOR_LIGHT_WEIGHT_FROG), 4 legs if its weight is more than 20 (MAX_WEIGHT_FOR_MED_WEIGHT_FROG), and 2 legs otherwise. The minimum value for weight is 1 (MIN_WEIGHT_FOR_FROG).
    Version:
    2022-10-28
    Author:
    Qi Yang
